== "Biased content" noticebox ==

Hey!

Sorry for not commenting on this earlier when the decision was made to add the noticebox, but we have reason to believe @[[User:Usr 1766f3ce-2cfb-4ac1-9b5d-06be1e938824|Kyuddle]] is involved with VRChat France which inherently makes this article biased in nature. Please reference our [[VRCWiki:Conflicts of interest|conflict of interest policy]]. People involved with a project should not be the ones creating and writing their wiki pages.

We have also reverted @[[User:Usr 1766f3ce-2cfb-4ac1-9b5d-06be1e938824|Kyuddle]]'s most recent change because this "bias" noticebox shouldn't be removed until a 3rd party is able to review the article, nor do we believe there should be marketing campaign references inserted into wiki links.

If we have misunderstood your affiliation with VRChat France, please feel free to reply here or chat with us on the VRChat Wiki Discord.

Thanks! - [[User:Usr e74229dd-6843-478e-be25-654453129010|big]] ([[User talk:Usr e74229dd-6843-478e-be25-654453129010|talk]]) 17:06, 25 August 2024 (UTC)

